{"tid":1738237,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗暴之戰】警方相應最低武力已提升至「致命」級別","createTime":"2019-11-19T07:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T12:01:31.000Z","uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ccce82fc55702cc1176acb95b50f2c902b91dffa","tid":1738237,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191119/large/1574142201_517d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191119%2Flarge%2F1574142201_517d.jpg&h=c03734b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反送中運動警民衝突不斷加劇，警方包圍理工大學行動，惹怒近10萬市民上街聲援抗爭者。警方應對升溫局勢，使用的「對等」及「相應」的「最低武力」已升級至「致命」級別。昨日多個衝突場合中，駐守警員不時舉起配槍瞄向抗爭者；有防暴警員更被拍攝到以衝鋒車掩護，高舉被形容為「最後武器」的AR-15步槍，瞄向理工大學位置的目標。<br />\n<br />\n昨深夜油麻地彌敦道一帶的衝突中，警方幾近以「放題式」向示威者發射多輪催淚彈，而示威者則投擲汽油彈還擊，部份參與驅散行動的防暴警同樣配備AR-15步槍追截示威者，不過有警員一度將一個金屬子彈匣遺留地上被記者發現，當時彈匣內已填裝實彈，顯示警隊已全面部署「致命」武器對付示威者。翻查資料，遭警員遺留地上的屬「STANAG彈匣」，可於多款5.56口徑步槍共用，除AR15步槍外，飛虎隊及反恐特勤隊使用的SIG516步槍亦可使用有關彈匣，而警方機動部隊配備的AR15步槍，使用的彈匣為裝填20發子彈版本。<br />\n<br />\n據傳媒所見，警方「速龍」隊員同樣配備發射實彈槍械，昨日於油麻地彌敦道參與清場，速龍隊員全程配備槍管位置裝有消音器的SIG 516半自動突擊步槍；另有警員則配備MP5衝鋒槍戒備。<br />\n<br />\n網上更流傳片段，警方昨晚衝突中除帶上「致命」實彈槍，更疑曾於鬧市中向示威者投擲震撼彈及閃光彈。根據網上片段所見，在衝突位置中突然傳出多下巨響，同時出現多次強勁閃光。另有傳媒亦拍攝到昨日參與行動的警員，胸前有SDU即飛虎隊襟章，身上並掛有兩枚疑似震撼彈物品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191119/60284544?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60284544%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4Mql6E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=6fb3a067\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60284544%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=d1e4d098\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191119/60284544?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"5c57be32b076863e2cf7f50ce9c66a61a25a6006","tid":1738237,"uid":340080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i3q7qfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi3q7qfJ.jpg&h=fd971ef9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34efdbfa2eaf74d77cace4fa91ae7ad224941027","tid":1738237,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"基本上現場搶到支  已經可以反攻"},{"pid":"1911568498794989bd9eec10fb3091c4777930c7","tid":1738237,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34efdbfa2eaf74d77cace4fa91ae7ad224941027","tid":1738237,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"基本上現場搶到支  已經可以反攻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:39:51.000Z","msg":"搶到枝即刻輸哂 攞正牌shoot to kill"},{"pid":"fc935250ed5daae9ef70b8b566a08e4fd33189cd","tid":1738237,"uid":144533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"除咗唔再捐錢俾無國界醫生之外，我哋可以做多樣野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1738004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1738004</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n#SOSHK"},{"pid":"40bcbbad17dbd875466f97b2f8f949c84aafee81","tid":1738237,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:43:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af754b4900e5431c5ec725416765a287b29280ba","tid":1738237,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1911568498794989bd9eec10fb3091c4777930c7","tid":1738237,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34efdbfa2eaf74d77cace4fa91ae7ad224941027","tid":1738237,"uid"